comments: I absolutely love your videos!!! But small suggestion can you have a small preview on what the next move is as I keep looking and constantly turning my head ending up losing balance 😢😢

Lidia, I absolutely love the dog! it made me smile throughout the workout, and it all weirdly pushed me to get to the very end! but pleeease, can you put some voiceovers? that would help a lot, thank you once again!😇
i am 14 years old but i do your workouts often and they are really very effective. i did your arm pilates and my arms are slim now... i am very greatfull to you thank you so much... keep going 😊😊
It was really nice that you added the stretches at the end, it’s a good moment to cool down and thank my body for everything it has done for me.Great video! 💗💌
I used to HATE working out, but your Pilates makes it the new highlight of my day! Thanks Lidia ❤
